N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6155.3 - Seminars

State Regulations

The fee to be charged for attending any seminar conducted
or sponsored by the Bureau of Prosecution Services shall be in an amount not to
exceed the projected per capita cost of conducting each seminar. Such fee shall
also include the cost of all seminar-related printed
material. Notes
